                            <comment id="14456828" author="david_syer" created="Thu, 23 Nov 2006 05:56:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I can&apos;t understand why this is categorised as &quot;minor&quot;.  Would it get more attention if someone bumped it up to &quot;major&quot;?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14453697" author="klaus.brunner" created="Thu, 30 Nov 2006 11:56:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;My workaround is to use &amp;lt;forkMode&amp;gt;always&amp;lt;/forkMode&amp;gt; in the surefire plugin config of the POM. Slows things down a bit, but at least the reports are coherent.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14453613" author="lauvigne" created="Fri, 16 Feb 2007 08:03:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;With workaround &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;forkMode&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;always&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/forkMode&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;  or &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;forkMode&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;pertest&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/forkMode&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt; , i have always the problem.&lt;br/&gt;
I am obliged to use version 2.2 because I use TestNG.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Why the patch is not applied, in 2.3-SNAPSHOT ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
